---
import CommunityHubLayout from '../layouts/CommunityHubLayout.astro';
---

<CommunityHubLayout
  title="Community | Wavey Dynamics"
  heading="COMMUNITY"
  subheading="Engaging with the engineering community."
  description="Wavey Dynamics community hub — social media content, podcast conversations, technical seminars, outreach programmes and Racecar Engineering Magazine features."
>

  <div class="space-y-14">

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Wavey Dynamics Online</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">To teach. To inspire. To entertain.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">We have a social media platform dedicated to bringing a new energy to technical and engineering content. Through Instagram and YouTube, you can expect content covering:</p>
        <ul class="wd-list mt-4 space-y-1 leading-relaxed list-none">
          <li>Product development insights</li>
          <li>Technical breakdowns</li>
          <li>Hands on Race engineering</li>
          <li>Product analysis</li>
          <li>Podcast style discussions</li>
          <li>Explanation of technical concepts</li>
          <li>The diversity of an engineering consultant</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">All social media is created and managed by Wavey Dynamics.</p>
        <a href="/online" class="inline-block mt-6 border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors"
          style="font-family:'Gotham Light',sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.08em;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;">Read More</a>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[218px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/community-online-thumb.jpg" alt="Wavey Dynamics Online" class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-gray-200" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Our Podcast</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">The Wavey Dynamics Podcast: A place for engineers, enthusiasts and fans to tune in to conversations with motorsport's finest engineers.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">What do you want to learn about today?</p>
        <a href="/podcast" class="inline-block mt-6 border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors"
          style="font-family:'Gotham Light',sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.08em;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;">Read More</a>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[218px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/community-podcast-thumb.png" alt="Wavey Dynamics Podcast" class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-gray-200" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Seminars &amp; Speaking</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">We've been invited to give a number of seminars and speaking events.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">These are great opportunities to pass on knowledge developed through our research and practical experience, as well as opportunity to connect with new generations of students, academia and the wider industry.</p>
        <a href="/seminars" class="inline-block mt-6 border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors"
          style="font-family:'Gotham Light',sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.08em;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;">Read More</a>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[218px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/outreach-seminar.jpg" alt="Seminars &amp; Speaking" class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-gray-200" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Outreach</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">The importance of inspiring a diverse talent base in our future generation of engineers can't be neglected.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">We make efforts to visit schools and exhibitions around London and the South East to demonstrate what engineers do, the possibilities ahead of them through careers in STEM and the power of motorsport.</p>
        <a href="/outreach" class="inline-block mt-6 border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors"
          style="font-family:'Gotham Light',sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.08em;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;">Read More</a>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[218px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/outreach-blacksteam.jpg" alt="Outreach" class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="border-gray-200" />

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 md:gap-10 items-start">
      <div class="flex-1">
        <h2>Racecar Engineering Magazine</h2>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">As a guest writer, a number of technical articles written by our director have been featured in Racecar Engineering magazine.</p>
        <p class="mt-4 leading-relaxed">Published features include:</p>
        <ul class="wd-list mt-4 space-y-1 leading-relaxed list-none">
          <li>Technical overview of modern motorsport suspension technology</li>
          <li>Suspension science roll-out</li>
          <li>Rig-based suspension development and kinematics</li>
          <li>A series on diagnosing setup in vehicle dynamics</li>
          <li>The subject of chassis &amp; suspension setup tools</li>
          <li>Thermal science behind traction strategy</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/rce" class="inline-block mt-6 border border-(--color-border) px-6 py-2 text-sm no-underline hover:border-(--color-accent) hover:text-(--color-accent) transition-colors"
          style="font-family:'Gotham Light',sans-serif;letter-spacing:0.08em;font-size:12px;text-transform:uppercase;">Read More</a>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full md:w-[218px] shrink-0">
        <img src="/images/pages/community-rce-thumb.jpg" alt="Racecar Engineering Magazine" class="w-full aspect-[4/5] object-cover" />
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>

</CommunityHubLayout>
